   "id": "a4c9546a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 9 interpretation\n",
    "\n",
    "The log transformation compresses extreme outliers and makes the difference between transported and non-transported passengers easier to see. Higher `RoomService`, `Spa`, and `VRDeck` spending usually appears more associated with not being transported. `FoodCourt` and `ShoppingMall` can still contain useful signal, but they are often weaker or noisier than the luxury-spending variables."
   ]
